# Order page (Habibi Direct)

Server-side WhatsApp delivery — customers never leave `/order`.

## Netlify environment variables

| Variable | Value | Notes |
|----------|-------|-------|
| `ORDER_WHATSAPP_TO` | `33677231846` | Inbox that receives orders (no `+`) |
| `CALLMEBOT_API_KEY` | from CallMeBot | Required for automatic send |

## CallMeBot setup (one-time)

1. On WhatsApp, send **"I allow callmebot to send me messages"** to **+34 644 52 42 02**.
2. Open [callmebot.com](https://www.callmebot.com/) and copy your API key for your number.
3. In Netlify → Site settings → Environment variables, add `CALLMEBOT_API_KEY`.
4. Redeploy.

Orders are sent to `ORDER_WHATSAPP_TO` only. The restaurant phone in `client.json` is never used for orders.
